edance.net/d?p=@byted-nodex/logger-core)](https://web-bnpm.byted.org/package/@byted-nodex/logger-core)\n\n[简体中文](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-nodex/blob/master/packages/logger-core/README.md) | [English](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-nodex/blob/master/packages/logger-core/README.en.md) | [CHANGELOG](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-nodex/blob/master/packages/logger-core/CHANGELOG.md)\n\n## @byted-nodex/logger-core\n\n### Install\n\n```bash\nnpm install @byted-nodex/logger-core\n```\n\n### Usage\n\n```ts\nimport { Logger } from '@byted-nodex/logger-core';\n\nconst logger = new Logger();\n\nlogger.trace('this is a trace log');\nlogger.debug('this is a debug log');\nlogger.info('this is an info log');\nlogger.warn('this is a warn log');\nlogger.error('this is an error log');\nlogger.fatal('this is a fatal log');\n```\n\n### API\n\n#### new Logger([options])\n\nInitialize a new Logger instance object\n\n- level：Optional，log level，the default is 'info'\n- enableConsoleLog：Optional, whether to enable console log output, the default is true\n- enableFileLog：Optional, whether to enable file log output, the default is true\n- consoleTransportOptions：Optional, parameters passed to console transport\n  - level：Optional, Transport log level\n- fileTransportOptions：Optional, parameters passed to file transport\n  - level：Optional, Transport log level\n  - file：Optional, log file path\n- callSiteFrameIndex: file：Optional, The stack depth is used to obtain the call log location. If you need to perform upper packaging based on @byted-nodex/logger, please pay attention to setting this value.\n\n#### logger.addTransport(name, transport)\n\nAdd a Transport\n\n- name：The name of the transport\n- transport：Transport instance\n\n#### logger.trace(message, [...splats])\n\nPrint a trace log message\n\n#### logger.debug(message, [...splats])\n\nPrint a debug log message\n\n#### logger.info(message, [...splats])\n\nPrint a info log message\n\n#### logger.warn(message, [...splats])\n\nPrint a warn log message\n\n#### logger.error(message, [...splats])\n\nPrint a error log message\n\n#### logger.fatal(message, [...splats])\n\nPrint a fatal log message\n\n#### logger.log([args])\n\n- args\n  - level: Required, log level, default is info\n  - msg: Optional, log message\n  - logId: Optional, logId, generally automatically set by the framework layer\n  - location: Optional, The log call stack location, which is automatically calculated by default.\n  - splats: Optional, log formatting parameter\n  - error: Optional, Error instance object\n  - tags: Optional, log tags, generally queried as an index\n","readmeFilename":"README.en.md","repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-nodex/tree/master/packages/logger-core"},"scripts":{"build":"tsc","build:watch":"tsc --watch","test":"jest --config ./jest.config.js --coverage","test:watch":"jest --config ./jest.config.js --coverage --watch"},"types":"./lib/index.d.ts","version":"1.1.6-beta.0"},"1.1.6-beta.1":{"_id":"@byted-nodex/logger-core@1.1.6-beta.1","_nodeVersion":"14.20.0","_npmUser":{"email":"wanggan.kk@bytedance.com","name":"wanggan.kk"},"_npmVersion":"lerna/undefined/node@v14.20.0+x64 (linux)","author":{"name":"wanggan"},"bugs":{"url":"https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-nodex/issues"},"dependencies":{"cron":"^2.1.0","dayjs":"^1.11.4","sonic-boom":"^3.0.0"},"description":"Super fast logger","devDependencies":{"@types/cron":"^2.0.0"},"dist":{"fileCount":30,"integrity":"sha512-4tyxC+/A7oAfieOUwhV2+vyUXVWQipyfGfSSRpwqJV5vfKUNVyRbxF/V20J5l5YdxUob70B8AcQxhIq8NA3Sgg==","shasum":"e14fbd13562e25804bf0a258cf8c67b76aa72103","size":9075,"tarball":"https://bnpm.byted.org/@byted-nodex/logger-core/-/logger-core-1.1.6-beta.1.tgz","unpackedSize":34995},"files":["lib","CHANGELOG.md","README.md","README.en.md"],"gitHead":"b3008e8ba4c8ca7c2c8ce66b424ff0d911d35725","keywords":["logger"],"main":"lib/index.js","maintainers":[{"email":"wanggan.kk@bytedance.com","name":"wanggan.kk"},{"email"